Package eu.casoftworks.jdroidlib.device

Contains classes used with and by JDroidLib to represent devices, their components and utilities that don't make sense in any other package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Battery
    Represents a Device's battery.
    BuildProp
    Device class; represents Device build properties.
    BusyBox
    Represents BusyBox installations on a Device
    Device
    Represents a physical device.
    FileSystem
    Represents the file system of a given device.
    PackageManager
    Device class; represents a device's package manager.
    SuperUser
    Represents a SuperUser installation on a given Device.
